; From Uji Bridge * From Uji Bridge, proceed along the approach path towards the Inner Shrine (Main Shrine), and you will find the Gojōden.<ref name="ic"/> Two subordinate shrines are located to the north: Yuki-no-Mikura is on the right, and {{ill|Misakadono-no-Kami|ja|御酒殿神|12=draft|12=draft}} is on the left.<ref name="ic"/><ref name="gk"/> Nearby is the sacred site of {{ill|Yotsuishi-no-Kami|ja|四至神|1=Miyanomeguri-no-Kami|12=draft|12=draft}}.<ref name="ic"/> == References == {{Reflist}}
